          "items": [
            {
              "answer": "It’s software that syncs your availability, rates, and reservations across multiple booking platforms, Airbnb, Booking.com, your own website, and more, in real time. No spreadsheets, no double-bookings.",
              "question": "What Is A Vacation-Rental Channel Manager?"
            },
            {
              "answer": "Plans start at $9 per month for one property. Every plan includes unlimited channels, automated messaging, and performance analytics.",
              "question": "How Much Does MyAllocator Cost?"
            },
            {
              "answer": "Whether you list on one OTA or ten, calendars can drift out of sync within minutes. MyAllocator updates every platform instantly, so guests always see accurate prices and availability, and you stay overbooking-free.",
              "question": "Why Does Hosts Need A Channel Manager?"
            },
            {
              "answer": "Absolutely. Connect both accounts (and any others) once; MyAllocator handles the rest, syncing every new booking, cancellation, or modification within seconds.",
